 earn by sharing their personal style to their personal networks.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1Gp_xDvCBVYXV4iAFXo_YnkfoumfZ06wStAODFd9oVCA/edit#slide=id.p4\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6589\" src=\"https://betterbots.utu.ai/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/mavenx.png\" width=\"283\" height=\"213\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThroughout the progression we start with the basic fundamentals of bot building, but then advance through evolving their existing webservice endpoints to custom API\'s that power a rich bot experience.  As we progress through the weeks this example will get more complex as we move towards a more complete end state - being that any bot is never complete![/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Curriculum\" tab_id=\"curriculum\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<ul class=\"section-content\">\r\n 	<li class=\"course-lesson\">\r\n<div class=\"meta-left\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"index\"><span class=\"label\">Lecture</span>1.1</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta-center2\">\r\n\r\n<a class=\"lesson-title\" href=\"http://docs.utu.ai/bot-anatomy-101\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Bot Anatomy 101</a>\r\n<div class=\"completed-button\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta\">10m</div></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"course-lesson\">\r\n<div class=\"meta-left\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"index\"><span class=\"label\">Lecture</span>1.2</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta-center2\">\r\n\r\n<a class=\"lesson-title\" href=\"http://docs.utu.ai/conversational-ui\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Conversational UI</a>\r\n<div class=\"completed-button\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta\">20m</div></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"course-lesson\">\r\n<div class=\"meta-left\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"index\"><span class=\"label\">Lecture</span>1.3</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta-center2\">\r\n\r\n<a class=\"lesson-title\" href=\"http://docs.utu.ai/natural-language-processing-nlp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noope