environment, but has been tested on Windows.  If you experience any environment issues please let us know!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_tabs][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Building your first bot with Botkit','','inherit','closed','closed','','1556-revision-v1','','','2017-05-24 11:17:25','2017-05-24 11:17:25','',1556,'https://betterbots.utu.ai/2017/05/24/1556-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1575,1,'2017-05-24 11:24:48','2017-05-24 11:24:48','[vc_row][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_tta_tabs][vc_tta_section title=\"Description\" tab_id=\"description\"][vc_column_text]uTu JavaScript SDK[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Curriculum\" tab_id=\"curriculum\"][vc_column_text][/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Instructors\" tab_id=\"instructors\"][vc_column_text][/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Tab\" tab_id=\"1495624874843-8c6d08d2-8b16\"][vc_column_text][/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_tabs][/vc_column][/vc_row]','uTu JavaScript SDK','','inherit','closed','closed','','1553-autosave-v1','','','2017-05-24 11:24:48','2017-05-24 11:24:48','',1553,'https://betterbots.utu.ai/2017/05/24/1553-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1576,1,'2017-05-24 11:25:01','2017-05-24 11:25:01','[vc_row][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_tta_tabs][vc_tta_section title=\"Description\" tab_id=\"description\"][vc_column_text]uTu JavaScript SDK[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Curriculum\" tab_id=\"curriculum\"][vc_column_text][/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Instructors\" tab_id=\"instructors\"][vc_column_text][/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Checklist\" tab_id=\"checklist\"][vc_column_text][/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_tabs][/vc_column][/vc_row]','uTu JavaScript SDK','','inherit','closed','closed','','1553-revision-v1','','','2017-05-24 11:25:01','2017-05-24 11:25:01','',1553,'https://betterbots.utu.ai/2017/05/24/1553-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1577,1,'2017-05-25 06:57:28','2017-05-25 06:57:28','[vc_row][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_tta_tabs active_section=\"1\"][vc_tta_section title=\"Description\" tab_id=\"description\"][vc_column_text]Even for experienced developers, basing your bot on a kit has a lot of benefits.  There is a lot of plumbing to be built, particularly when connecting to multiple channels, and leveraging the benefits of a kit community like <a href=\"https://howdy.ai/botkit/\">Botkit</a> (and supported by <a href=\"https://howdy.ai/\">howdy.ai</a>) can get you jumpstarted.\r\n\r\nThis course starts at the beginning.  Basic familiarity with JavaScript and Node.Js useful, but we will cover all the details.  By the end of this class, you will have:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>A thorough understanding of how to properly structure a bot</li>\r\n 	<li>How to get up and running with a <a href=\"https://howdy.ai/botkit/\">Botkit</a> bot</li>\r\n 	<li>Coded AI, NLP, and Listener modules</li>\r\n 	<li>Instrumented your bot with <a href=\"https://utu.ai/\">uTu.ai</a> for advanced analytics and training</li>\r\n 	<li>Efficiently multi-homed your bot</li>\r\n 	<li>Communicated with your bot over FB Messenger and Amazon Alexa.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Sample Code Overview</strong>\r\n\r\nCode is structured around the story of building a bot for Mavenx.com, a site that empowers shoppers to earn by sharing their personal style to their personal networks.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1Gp_xDvCBVYXV4iAFXo_YnkfoumfZ06wStAODFd9oVCA/edit#slide=id.p4\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6589\" src=\"https://betterbots.utu.ai/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/mavenx.png\" width=\"283\" height=\"213\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThroughout the progression we start with the basic fundamentals of bot building, but then advance through evolving their existing webservice endpoints to custom API\'s that power a rich bot experience.  As we progress through the weeks this example will get more complex as we move towards a more complete end state - being that any bot is never complete![/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Curriculum\" tab_id=\"curriculum\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<ul class=\"section-content\">\r\n 	<li class=\"course-lesson\">\r\n<div class=\"meta-left\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"index\"><span class=\"label\">Lecture</span>1.1</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta-center2\">\r\n\r\n<a class=\"lesson-title\" href=\"http://docs.utu.ai/bot-anatomy-101\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Bot Anatomy 101</a>\r\n<div class=\"completed-button\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta\">10m</div></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"course-lesson\">\r\n<div class=\"meta-left\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"index\"><span class=\"label\">Lecture</span>1.2</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta-center2\">\r\n\r\n<a class=\"lesson-title\" href=\"http://docs.utu.ai/conversational-ui\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Conversational UI</a>\r\n<div class=\"completed-button\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta\">20m</div></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"course-lesson\">\r\n<div class=\"meta-left\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"index\"><span class=\"label\">Lecture</span>1.3</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta-center2\">\r\n\r\n<a class=\"lesson-title\" href=\"http://docs.utu.ai/natural-language-processing-nlp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Natural Language Processing (NLP)</a>\r\n<div class=\"completed-button\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta\">15m</div></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"course-lesson\">\r\n<div class=\"meta-left\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"index\"><span class=\"label\">Lecture</span>1.4</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta-center2\">\r\n\r\n<a class=\"lesson-title\" href=\"http://docs.utu.ai/listener-botkit-alexa\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Listener Botkit – Alexa</a>\r\n<div class=\"completed-button\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta\">15m</div></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"course-lesson\">\r\n<div class=\"meta-left\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"index\"><span class=\"label\">Lecture</span>1.5</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta-center2\">\r\n\r\n<a class=\"lesson-title\" href=\"http://docs.utu.ai/botkit-artificial-intelligence\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Botkit – Artificial Intelligence</a>\r\n<div class=\"completed-button\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta\">20m</div></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"course-lesson\">\r\n<div class=\"meta-left\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"index\"><span class=\"label\">Lecture</span>1.6</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta-center2\">\r\n\r\n<a class=\"lesson-title\" href=\"http://docs.utu.ai/web-services\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Web Services</a>\r\n<div class=\"completed-button\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta\">5m</div></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"course-lesson\">\r\n<div class=\"meta-left\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"index\"><span class=\"label\">Lecture</span>1.7</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta-center2\">\r\n\r\n<a class=\"lesson-title\" href=\"http://docs.utu.ai/conversant-tracking\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Conversant Tracking</a>\r\n<div class=\"completed-button\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta\">30m</div></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"course-lesson\">\r\n<div class=\"meta-left\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"index\"><span class=\"label\">Lecture</span>1.8</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta-center2\">\r\n\r\n<a class=\"lesson-title\" href=\"http://docs.utu.ai/hosting\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Hosting</a>\r\n<div class=\"completed-button\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta\">15m</div></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"course-lesson\">\r\n<div class=\"meta-left\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"index\"><span class=\"label\">Lecture</span>1.9</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta-center2\">\r\n\r\n<a class=\"lesson-title\" href=\"http://docs.utu.ai/bot-security\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Bot Security</a>\r\n<div class=\"completed-button\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta\">10m</div></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"course-lesson\">\r\n<div class=\"meta-left\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"index\"><span class=\"label\">Lecture</span>1.10</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta-center2\">\r\n\r\n<a class=\"lesson-title\" href=\"http://docs.utu.ai/multichannel-bots\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Multichannel Bots</a>\r\n<div class=\"completed-button\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"meta\">30m</div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Instructors\" tab_id=\"instructors\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class=\"author-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"author-avatar\"><img class=\"avatar avatar-110 photo\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/baf7907350fd64ef9f966b220ed86f5d?s=110&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g\" srcset=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/baf7907350fd64ef9f966b220ed86f5d?s=220&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g 2x\" alt=\"\" width=\"110\" height=\"110\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"author-bio\">\r\n<div class=\"author-top\"><a class=\"name\" href=\"https://betterbots.utu.ai/lp-profile/Marcus/courses/\">\r\nMarcus Tewksbury\r\n</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"author-description\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Checklist\" tab_id=\"checklist\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div id=\"tab-course-checklist\" class=\"tab-pane active\">\r\n\r\nThis course is designed to be, or at least start at, a 100 level.  We’ve tried to make getting started as simply as possible – even at times packaging away some details to focus on the bigger picture.  With that said, to do the lessons you will need:\r\n\r\n1. <a href=\"https://git-scm.com/book/en/v2/Getting-Started-Installing-Git\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-6571\" src=\"https://betterbots.utu.ai/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/git-hub-icon-300x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a> 2. <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/download/package-manager/\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http://seeklogo.com/images/N/nodejs-logo-FBE122E377-seeklogo.com.png\" width=\"41\" height=\"46\" /></a> 3. <a href=\"http://blog.npmjs.org/post/85484771375/how-to-install-npm\"><img class=\"alignnone \" src=\"https://www.npmjs.com/static/images/npm-logo.svg\" width=\"113\" height=\"44\" /></a>\r\n\r\nAlso, if you haven’t already done so, you should install a development environment.  For the purposes of the lessons we will be using:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://flight-manual.atom.io/getting-started/sections/installing-atom/\"><img class=\"alignnone \" src=\"https://cdn-business.discourse.org/uploads/github_atom/490/d8548f4ce56f1599.png\" width=\"197\" height=\"197\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe code repo was developed in a Unix environment, but has been tested on Windows.  If you experience any environment issues please let us know!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_tabs][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Building your first bot with Botkit','','inherit','closed','closed','','1556-revision-v1','','','2017-05-25 06:57:28','2017-05-25 06:57:28','',1556,'https://betterbots.utu.ai/2017/05/25/1556-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1579,1,'2017-05-31 11:17:28','2017-05-31 11:17:28','','Event Detail','','publish','closed','closed','','acf_event-detail','','','2017-05-31 11:17:28','2017-05-31 11:17:28','',0,'https://betterbots.utu.ai/?post_type=acf&#038;p=1579',0,'acf','',0),(1580,1,'2017-05-31 11:21:36','2017-05-31 11:21:36','We would like to invite you to join us in our next Meetup about Alexa Bot!\r\n\r\nThis hands on session will cover the basics of creating a bot for Amazon Alexa. We will cover a potential development workflow, setup on Amazon, and instrumenting a production environment for further improvement. The Meetup will be directed by Jimmie Butler, a co-founder at Utu Intelligence, a company that is building a bot analytics platform, and working to help developers build better bots.\r\n\r\n<b>*Please be aware that the conference will be 100% in English.</b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nYou should come to this session if you:\r\n\r\n• Want to learn how to build an Amazon Alexa powered bot\r\n\r\n• Want to learn common patterns used in building bots\r\n\r\n• Want to explore the possibilities of working with a conversational UI\r\n\r\n• Want to learn about the benefits of deploying your bot cross platforms\r\n\r\nAlso, come to the session with…\r\n\r\n• Comfort with JavaScript\r\n\r\n• Comfort with git and github\r\n\r\n• A laptop tricked out with your IDE of choice\r\n\r\nWe hope to see you there!\r\n\r\nhttps://www.meetup.com/medellin-java/events/238155228','Medellin – My First Bot in 90min','','inherit','closed','closed','','1456-revision-v1','','','2017-05-31 11:21:36','2017-05-31 11:21:36','',1456,'https://betterbots.utu.ai/2017/05/31/1456-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1581,1,'2017-05-31 11:24:05','2017-05-31 11:24:05','<h4>EVENT DESCRIPTION</h4>\r\nThis is a hands on session where we will explore the possibilities of communication channels by building our own, fully functional bot in under 90 minutes. Some coding experience helpful, but not required. We will start with an overview of the conversational space and why you should care. Then we will move into the anatomy of a bot where we will explore concepts like Natural Language Processing (NLP) and Artificial Intelligence (AI) as we get into code, showing you how to instrument your bot for deeper understanding and conversing with it on Amazon Alexa or Facebook Messenger.\r\n<h4>EVENT CONTENT</h4>\r\n<ul class=\"thim-list-content\">\r\n 	<li>Want to explore the possibilities of working with a conversational UI</li>\r\n 	<li>Want to learn how to build an AI logic tree</li>\r\n 	<li>Want to learn how to train a bot with NLP and custom intents</li>\r\n 	<li>Want to better understand the type of data available in the conversant channel</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n<h4>PREREQUISITES</h4>\r\